We can just, like, look for solutions once we're

00:21:36.820 --> 00:21:41.950
faced with them to somehow comply with it and see what we

00:21:42.090 --> 00:21:44.040
can do to not screw everybody.

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:45.040
No.

